                    <p>Backend is the behind-the-scenes of every project. Hidden from our eyes, it's responsible for making things work. With solid experience in Node.js, AJAX, APIs, and TypeScript, I'll help you build the backbone of your web app from scratch or integrate it into your existing website.</p>
