                    <p>Frontend is everything you see on your screen. It's pretty and allows you to interact with the behind-the-scenes, that would otherwise be one hell of a mess for you as a user.</p>
                    <p>It's crucial for the client-side to be intuitive and functional. Luckily for you, I'm equipped with a powerful combination of React, Tailwind & HTML CSS to help you achieve it!</p>
                </div>
